<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink353">
<l>erikkoṭik kavaiiya cevvarai pōlac</l>
<l>cuṭarppūṇ viḷaṅku mēnteḻi lakala</l>
<l>nīyiṉitu muyaṅka vantaṉar</l>
<l>māyiruñ cōlai malaiyiṟan tōrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The man who crossed mountains with large dark groves </l>
<l>returned for you to embrace sweetly </l>
<l>his handsome eminent chest shining with glowing jewels </l>
<l>like a red mountain, embraced by flames of fire. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
